[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Responsibilities/activities[bold]The BIS Sustainability Committee will: 
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Report to the Executive Board on the performance of BIS against its sustainability commitments and progress in embedding sustainability into policy making
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Review and make recommendations to the Executive Board on further development of BIS’s sustainability commitments, governance and activities to support its overall ambitions
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Contribute sustainability content to the BIS operational plan, business planning, developing and recommending sustainability business performance measures (where none exist).
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Contribute to reporting on sustainability across government including: BIS annual report and accounts, annual Greener Government report
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Develop actions plans, overseeing implementation and monitoring performance across BIS in order to achieve greener government targets and measures set out in the Operational Plan
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Benchmark BIS’s sustainability performance against partner organisations and peers.
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Communicate sustainability activities and plans to staff and, where relevant, external stakeholders 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]These responsibilities will be discharged through Committee Members’ co-ordinataion of the following themes: 
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Sustainable Operations
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Sustainable Procurement
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Sustainable Policy making
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Meeting frequency[bold]Quarterly or as required at the discretion of the Chair.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Reporting [bold]The Committee will report quarterly to the Operations Committee on sustainability performance, and to the Executive Board every six months and annually through the BIS Annual Report and Accounts.
